INPUT
--> [Multiplier
      gain: dB 40
    ]
--> [LowPass
      high_cut: % 5
      mix: % 90
    ]
--> [LowPass
      high_cut: %% 50
      mix: % 60
    ]
--> [Delayer
      delay: 11000
      feedback: % 60
      mix: % 10
    ]
--> [Compressor
      ratio: 2
      threshold: dB -30
      attack: % 5
      mix: % 70
    ]
--> OUTPUT

Simple warm tone simulator.
